Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:27.17,Karaoke-Up,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf27}頑{\kf24}張っ{\kf31}て　{\kf16}張{\kf14}り{\kf21}切っ{\kf32}て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:27.17,Karaoke-Up-Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf27}Gan{\kf24}bat{\kf31}te,　{\kf16}ha{\kf14}ri{\kf21}kit{\kf32}te
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:27.17,Karaoke-Down-Trans,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best, be on high,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.34,Karaoke-Up,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf18}ま、{\kf29}ダー{\kf11}リ{\kf7}ン{\kf23}ダー{\kf17}リ{\kf3}ン{\kf8}プ{\kf60}リー{\kf41}ズ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.34,Karaoke-Up-Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf18}Ma, {\kf29}daa{\kf11}ri{\kf7}n {\kf23}daa{\kf17}ri{\kf3}n {\kf8}pu{\kf60}rii{\kf41}zu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.34,Karaoke-Down-Trans,,0000,0000,0000,,well darling darling please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, this problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I was just asked!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? No, I haven't been sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:55.48,Episode Name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(211,192)}The Problem\N With Motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my English textbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you go and borrow Kagami's? They already had English, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you're always so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should check the day before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa does forget quite a lot of things, now doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Konata, you really don't forget things like textbooks, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be surprising to you, but I do take such things seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always leave my textbooks at school beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, it was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly taking it not seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you leave your textbooks at school always, you can't review anything, now can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I dont study at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you really don't take anything home before the day before the test...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Konata is good at getting the points, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be why I always forget my homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about you it's not about forgetting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's about not trying at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please, show your Modern Japanese homework for today's afternoon lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asking already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought about it, but you're in the same class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so go ask Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san is a too good person, which makes it even harder to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do somehow understand, but that's not satisfactory...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Izumi.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Izumi!'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a bit slown down as I was helping a person in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person always moves around together with me, but I just couldn't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hee...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was nice to say things like 'I'm OK with it, so let's break up.', but the other five...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. She's already using a word that might be unusual, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,already took pairs, leaving only him, so it leaves a bad aftertaste, now doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}...only now does it get so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been in a party in a long time already, so at such time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said 'Let's all help him!'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now friends are a great thing to have, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, was that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you had an all-nighter in an internet game yesterday, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been an eternity after I fell out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Izumi.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Izumi!'
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STOP! I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl rushed into me before the shopping area...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl suddenly took my hand and started running...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when asked she told me that she had stolen taiyaki,...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was natural of her to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did think about why I had to be dragged into it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. KEY's Kanon, anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I had no options, I entered a cafe in order to hide from the taiyaki seller...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so many places to intervene with 'uguu'...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Ayu-neta, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it would be wrong to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an educator, as a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww, got summer cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. 38.2 Celsius is 100.76 Fahrenheit, Americans...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Izumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Aww, sensei... I'm sorry but I'd like to take a sick leave"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Hey hey, did you overdo with games again?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Don't just try to use the same way every time!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I'd like to call myself in sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Now you wouldn't say something like summer cold, right?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The winter's gone and there's a good weather..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"so don't just always say something like 'I'm lazy', come here fast!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I got a full 'ookami shounen'- treatment yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. ookami shounen - the boy who cried wolf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you got on yourself by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan, are you OK already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like my fever has gotten down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my throat still stings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so Kona-chan breaths through the nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she does do that through the throat, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you usually do it through the nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kona-chan has a bigger rate of breathing through the throat,...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, when the cold virus gets into your throat you get throat cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when it gets in through the nose you get nose cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so people who get throat cold, like, have a bigger propability to get the virus through throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaa... Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At such times let's leave it to Miyuki to burst the bubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the birthday party, but wouldn't you do it at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot I can't take a step...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Aww... But we're baking cookies here right now..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Happy Birthday!'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa plus the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't turn it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on behalf of your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san and Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might not be of your liking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paired earrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did think about a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I couldn't pretty much couldn't decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, I, too, will give my humble belongings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Brigade Leader armband!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Do I have to spell SOS-dan to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I put something like this on myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... And I thought it would suit you perfectly'ga, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ToHeart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. ToHeart - a passion of mine; At Cospa those cost 31,290 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear it with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't arrange sisters and make them do cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really think that it differs from the ones at our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's troublesome. When it just is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you just get annoyed. Like with the smelly ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's someone's birthday so try to restrain yourself for just even a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cookies that Tsukasa made are delicious, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this time I was making them with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah...tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really weird that after I heard that there's a feeling that some of these are not so delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be Kagami's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're here, come on and eat some cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only on her birthday did I meet the devotedly working Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:07:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, don't you just fuss about how to cut the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when you cut it into many pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are the things like 'Who will eat the strawberry on the top?'...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or 'Who will eat the plate chocolate?'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you all like plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I cut off the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really think it's Kagami's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What isn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuwaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strawberry's pretty small...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh what is it? Do I have cake on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only got once more affirmed of Kagami's charm-dazo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. a reference to a popular manga/anime Crayon Shin-Chan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously resemble him, so just stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer vacation this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea, the pool, the summer festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were there any other standard events?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you speak of summer, the festival that is held two times per year...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The longest rise of the night sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the comike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no... That's only you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}tn. Comike - Comic Market, a twice-in-a-year event at the Makuhari Messe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The red hair?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There could be different events for different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Existing and, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, do you have any plans for the summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment we have plans to go abroad again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah, 'Again this year'?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she have the cash, this bourgeois of-a-kind!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a yoghurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. There is a yoghurt brand called Bulgaria's yoghurt in Japan, this is a pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did say that you started working at a costume cafe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't such places impossible to get into if you haven't got good looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I, too, always had a thing with the fact I had no breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until there was a game, in which it was said that: 'Flat chest is a status item!', 'A thing of Great Value!'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. the game is SHUFFLE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:06.22,Karaoke-Up-Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,100)}Flat\Nchest\Nis a\Nstatus\Nitem\N!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:06.22,Karaoke-Up-Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(62,144)}A thing \Nof\N Great Value!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. When you think about it that way, there are such needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm something valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I'd like to know why games have such strong self-confidence..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think that I'm OK, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, with you... The end-of-term tests are almost here, are you OK with just playing games?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd turn that passion even a bit towards studies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd get higher scores, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"If she's so easily affected, then if some games that'd recommend studying would come out, it'd turn out pretty unbelievable..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Moe Drill, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Mentioned game is the Raki*Suta Moe Doriru for the DS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dotano?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately there are many crimes with young guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those are like, when you ask someone in the neighborhood they all arrange their speeches:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"He was usually quiet and obedient... didn't seem to be a person who'd do such things."{\i0}. that's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Higurashi no Naku Koro ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's just how treacherous the appearance can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd cause some incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I was sure sure she'd do something some day."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd testify it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hun!?\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot I just can't make myself do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Well, I do understand the feeling very well,...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're saying that you don't want to do anything the whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-10\fs18\fnArial\bord0\c&H000000&\fscy210\pos(388,217)\alpha&H80&}The Hiiragi Household
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ossu! Are you progressing with your test studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I was cleaning my room right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Huh?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, when you're starting something don't you just want to clean and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Well, even though I understand the feeling, 'try your best'."{\i0}]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let's do even a bit today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuaaaaaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a break for only 30 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot keep my concentration...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already such time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For another 30 minutes, only 30 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't it the time for Haruhi to start already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that Nagato's long talk could just be corner-cutting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Notice the 2ch.net forums on the background...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... The YaXXXXXX nowadays is not that good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Yamamoto - director of many SHNY episodes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hufu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muwaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaa, they're 'discussing' it already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, is it already two-o'-clock? This day was somehow not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep a bit and study in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wake up at five...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could sleep for three hours from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end I just wasted time on anime and manga and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very Kona-chan- like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Konata's preference of manga and games is a bit weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read a lot of shounen magazines and your main is gyaruge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. Shounen - young boys / guys - here as 'smthng for XXX'; gyaruge - 'gal games', one way of saying 'bishoujo games', a type of 'eroge' - although 'gyaruge' are not always 'ero'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father reads a lot of manga and plays games, so I'm influenced by that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking next to him from the days while I was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand shounen magazines, but 'gyaruge' and 'bishoujyo-ge' before his own daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of a father is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, doesn't your mother say anything about both father and child being like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, well it's because there's no mother at our place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She passed away when I was really small...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that I'm always doing chores, so I'm a lot better at them than Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say unnecessary things when it's already hard enough to comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, too, is good at cooking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how good I am at it, but I just love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems rich, so she could be not so good with housework and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Cooking, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth I only help from time to time,...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it's embarrassing, I'm not that good at housework...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oo, so I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But Miyuki is just too good at other things, her levels are so different...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you shouldn't take her minuses literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about our teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to live by herself, but has quite a lax image.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays you can live somehow even without knowing how to cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have conbini and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huuuh....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can gulp, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It'd be nice if you'd stop those too fitting jokes!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. It's Kyon-style "...yamete itadakitai..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Tsukasa still has my dictionary borrowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, I'm sorry but return my dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit of a room cleaning because of mood change...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuwaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ossu! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well we're all thinking about the new summer menu at the place I work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you have such?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, did you just give up about the tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about super-spicy raamen? Hot stuff is the best for hot season!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. raamen - Japanese wheat noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh... Try to think of a bit more cafe-like menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what about super-spicy parfait?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you just stop with those spinal reflex- ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just don't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh why doesn't our school have swimming lessons even if it has a pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me it's a bit helpful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I just cannot open my eyes in water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't really swim... even though it is embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Your weak spots are always somehow not fair..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hn! Finally the Comp Festival has started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, now that I think of it, because of this I started working part-time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Festival, now is it... somehow it's been so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying old jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when the customers join us and get the tension up,...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just feel that you're arousing the overall feeling of the festival, now don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That heat... Try to move it towards the school even for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:17:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fall asleep... I should just read a book until I get sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one that I just bought, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no longer the time to sleep - it's the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now it feels like I could sleep well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand why you have to cut the power while near the priority seats, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the thing with pacemakers and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it basically not allowed to talk on phones in trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that because you'll annoy people that aren't talking with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, but you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there just people that have a loud voice even without phones...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,towards both young and old?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you do miko or something during the summer festival like when visiting the shrine for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. 'miko' - a maiden in the service of a Shinto shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, we're always not doing it in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you say about it it's almost that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Aren't you dieting now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Nope, it could be the fatigue from the studying, but after I weighted myself yesterday... I had lost weight!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"So I'm beginning to think that it's OK already and stuff..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast! Or should I say weak!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh, Kagami - what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got back up in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you carelessly eat snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's a 'senryuu'...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. 'senryuu' - A type of short literature derived from haiku, not restricted by haiku word types and consisting of 17 symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:41.69,Kokuban,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c0\fs30\pos(345,76)\alpha&H32&\fad(1269,0)}The weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.69,Kokuban,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c0\fs30\alpha&H32&\fad(1190,0)\pos(414,204)}It got \Nback up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.69,Kokuban,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c0\fs30\alpha&H32&\fad(1070,0)\pos(414,260)}in an\N instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I ate just, just a bit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get so fussed over a few kilos, even though...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't even get on your looks if you gain a kilo or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why them women are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right you should be a woman, too, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Star
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LUCKY CHANNEL!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting on this week, Lucky Channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you all been energetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, always on 120% of cheerfulness, Kogami Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through a 'Nyoro-n', it's me - the assistant - Shiraishi Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. 'nyoron' - It's in the Wikipedia, LOL...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, was th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't friggin' enter and interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aahh... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no 'Gaki no Tsukai', so come on - remember your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. 'Gaki no Tsukai' - a Japanese comedy show
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to leave this job that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk tsk tsk tsk tsk tsk tsk tsk tsk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah! I have no excuses, I will try my best, the very best I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,jya-jyaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a big announcement for you all again -desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who entered on Comp's November edition! Akira's 'get fashionable'- plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got so much mail from you all so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... well, it feels that there was another plan like that in there, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for som much reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"At the comeback I'll do that, pii-!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that jokes from the eighties will not be really understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I will present you one of the ideas judged strictly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the Akira's 'get fashionable'- plan from Sappishi Chirii-san, Saitama prefecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kagami-san's 'twin tail' looks very good on her, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't you try it, too, Akira-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin tail... That's so go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuwaah! It's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, long hair is the life of all women!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you split it in two, it just gives you... this pretty feeling, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it or not, with Akira-sama's hairlength that's not possible, not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, it's not that good to just make your hair long...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}A-Akira-sama, we're almost there, almost...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}we're almost there, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Well, that's... the person inside...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}The talking of the person inside, it's not Akira-sama! Do you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Heey?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's really weigthy, plus it's really hard to lower them right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So to speak the truth it's not popular right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men always easily say that they prefer women with long hair,...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but how much effort, labour and money do you think did it take to keep this style?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if I do it this much, no-one ever marks it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huwaa! It's already the time to part!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would Akira look if she'd do twin tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's continue about that on the radio or on the site!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye-piii!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look foward for the next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say about 'attitude'?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snapping on all the time,...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you get so worked up on the first comment about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No such thing, I was just thinking if people would understand noripii nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, excuse me, let's go on a new style...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, they're, like doing Shiraishi Minoru auditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that for the first time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems pretty funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, I'm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To say the real me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan, you're unbelievable! You can sing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, only anime songs, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really sing well, using many impersonations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fast rule of anime songs is to trace the original version as well as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should sing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,onee-chan, what will you sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name just passed on the screen, but I didn't know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Miyuki, you don't know this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems like Kagami can't say so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I've heard this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}tn. The OP song 'Seeraa-fuku to kikanjyuu' from the 1982/2006 TV series and a 1981 movie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did watch the drama with me until recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, was that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow fancy the movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, an old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:46.16,Karaoke-Up,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8F83FF&}さよならは別れの言葉じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:46.16,Karaoke-Up-Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8F83FF&}Sayonara wa wakare no kotoba jyanakute...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! She's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is the best in singing within our sisters.
